OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773668262
OL,3,CDriver jailed over killing four-year-
OL,4,Cold in crash after Eid celebrations
OL,6,FA driver who killed a four-year-old
OL,7,Fgirl while she was walking home after
OL,8,Fan Eid celebration has been jailed for
OL,9,F"careless driving".
OL,11,FJavonnie Tavener, 23, also seriously
OL,12,Finjured two others while trying to
OL,13,Fovertake at speed on Upper Highgate
OL,14,FStreet at around 9pm on 14 April 2024.
OL,16,FMayar Yahia was killed in the
OL,17,Faccident, with her mother Sara and
OL,18,Fanother mother, Awadia Hammed, also
OL,19,Fseriously hurt.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
