OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773668262
OL,3,CDriver jailed over killing four-year-
OL,4,Cold in crash after Eid celebrations
OL,6,FTavener fled the scene and was later
OL,7,Ffound to have been using his phone and
OL,8,Funinsured to drive.
OL,10,FMonths after the collision, Tavener
OL,11,Fused his mobile phone to search
OL,12,Fdriving negligence, and the potential
OL,13,Fban for causing death by careless
OL,14,Fdriving, despite telling police he did
OL,15,Fnot own a mobile phone.
OL,17,FThe crash left the family and
OL,18,Fcommunity in shock and triggered a
OL,19,Fwave of road safety demonstrations and
OL,20,Fcalls for tougher enforcement.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
