CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773668262
OL,3,CDriver jailed over killing four-year-
OL,4,Cold in crash after Eid celebrations
OL,6,FIn a tribute, Yahia's family said:
OL,7,F"Mayar was an extraordinary child. She
OL,8,Fwas full of love and always smiling,
OL,9,Fkind to everyone and made friends
OL,10,Feasily.
OL,12,F"She was cheerful and bright, and she
OL,13,Fbrought happiness to everyone around
OL,14,Fher at home, in her school and her
OL,15,Fneighbourhood.
OL,17,F"There are no words that can truly
OL,18,Fdescribe how special she was, or how
OL,19,Fmuch we miss her.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773668262
OL,3,CDriver jailed over killing four-year-
OL,4,Cold in crash after Eid celebrations
OL,6,F"Losing Mayar has been the most
OL,7,Fpainful experience of our lives. It's
OL,8,Fnot just our loss; it's a loss to her
OL,9,Ffriends and to the whole community.
OL,11,F"We hope this tragedy serves as a
OL,12,Freminder to everyone of the importance
OL,13,Fof driving safely and responsibly. No
OL,14,Fone deserves to lose a loved one like
OL,15,Fthis.
OL,17,F"Mayar will always be in our hearts."
OL,19,FOn Friday, Tavener was sentenced to
OL,20,Fthree years and 10 months.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773668262
OL,3,CDriver jailed over killing four-year-
OL,4,Cold in crash after Eid celebrations
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Paul Hughes, from
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police, said: "Mayar was
OL,8,Fjust four years old when her life was
OL,9,Ftragically taken away from her.
OL,11,F"She was walking back with her family
OL,12,Fand friends after celebrating Eid.
OL,14,F"Pedestrians should be reassured of
OL,15,Fprotection when walking on the
OL,16,Fpavement and a split-second decision
OL,17,Fby Tavener to overtake where he did
OL,18,Fhas led to this tragic chain of events.
OL,20,F"He then made no efforts to ring the
OL,21,Femergency services.
OL,26,@oD@]OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773668262
OL,3,CDriver jailed over killing four-year-
OL,4,Cold in crash after Eid celebrations
OL,6,F"I would urge all drivers to think
OL,7,Fabout this incident and how those
OL,8,Fdecisions can have such catastrophic
OL,9,Fconsequences."
OL,11,FDuring the sentencing, Judge Peter
OL,12,FCooke said Tavener sought to evade
OL,13,Fresponsibility and made the 'extremely
OL,14,Fcallous decision' to walk away and not
OL,15,Fattempt to help.
OL,17,FHe was sentenced to an extra 18 months
OL,18,Ffor an unrelated assault, bringing his
OL,19,Ftotal jail time to five years and four
OL,20,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
